Not,affiliated,with,IMDb,the,IMDB,API,is,a,service,which,provides,access,to,most,of,IMDB,s,data,the,most,popular,and,authoritative,source,of,information,on,movies,TV,and,celebrities,Currently,the,IMDB,s,dataset,can,be,downloaded,but,an,API,is,not,available,to,retrieve,information,This,API,allows,developers,to,access,this,data,using,RESTful,calls,and,provides,responses,in,XML,and,JSON